title: Robot Wars Extreme (2001-2003)
description:
Robot Wars Extreme was a spin-off robot combat show from the main robot wars series. It contains a series of different battles, grudge matches, etc, without a defined tournament. It was made by the BBC from 2001 to 2003 and there were 2 seasons made. 

I've gathered up everything I could find, and organised it with FileBot according to tvdb listings.

I've managed to track down all of it here, but I've not watched through it all yet.

If you find any errors, please let me know, I try and keep this as accurate as possible!

Please seed if possible, I try and seed as best I can, but there's only so much I can do alone
